<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>helios::engine::mechanics::spawn::manager</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Managers<sp/>for<sp/>spawn<sp/>and<sp/>despawn<sp/>request<sp/>processing.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>namespace<sp/>contains<sp/>the<sp/>SpawnManager<sp/>which<sp/>handles<sp/>the<sp/>actual<sp/>spawning<sp/>and<sp/>despawning<sp/>of<sp/>GameObjects<sp/>from<sp/>pools.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Managers</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Manager<sp/>|<sp/>Purpose<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---------|---------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`SpawnManager`<sp/>|<sp/>Processes<sp/>spawn/despawn<sp/>requests,<sp/>manages<sp/>pool<sp/>lifecycle<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Responsibilities</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>SpawnManager:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Receives<sp/>SpawnRequest<sp/>and<sp/>DespawnRequest<sp/>instances</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>Queues<sp/>requests<sp/>for<sp/>deferred<sp/>processing</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>During<sp/>flush:<sp/>processes<sp/>despawns<sp/>first,<sp/>then<sp/>spawns</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>Uses<sp/>GameObjectFactory<sp/>to<sp/>populate<sp/>pools</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">5.<sp/>Registers<sp/>as<sp/>PoolRequestHandler<sp/>for<sp/>its<sp/>assigned<sp/>pool</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Usage</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto<sp/>factory<sp/>=<sp/>std::make_unique&lt;GameObjectFactory&gt;(...);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto<sp/>manager<sp/>=<sp/>std::make_unique&lt;SpawnManager&gt;(poolId,<sp/>std::move(factory));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Initialize<sp/>and<sp/>register<sp/>with<sp/>GameWorld</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">manager-&gt;init(gameWorld);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Register<sp/>as<sp/>manager<sp/>in<sp/>game<sp/>loop</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">gameLoop.addManager(std::move(manager));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
